of hiring me back.

278
00:14:54,159 --> 00:14:57,253
I told you. I'm content
at home and at work.

279
00:14:57,329 --> 00:14:59,263
But you're not
content with content.

280
00:14:59,331 --> 00:15:01,356
It's why you got sucked
into those stock scams,

281
00:15:01,433 --> 00:15:03,697
why you cheated
on the wife you love.

282
00:15:03,769 --> 00:15:05,259
