other doctors to give it to him.

289
00:15:18,517 --> 00:15:20,280
Metaphorically speaking,
you're a Heimlich addict.

290
00:15:20,352 --> 00:15:21,649
And you're an
addiction addict.

291
00:15:21,720 --> 00:15:23,517
Right now, your drug of
choice is your old team,

292
