them separate.

316
00:16:46,438 --> 00:16:49,498
And that's why our
personal life doesn't exist.

317
00:16:51,110 --> 00:16:52,134
None of that has to...

318
00:16:52,211 --> 00:16:54,270
I can't work with you.

319
