You already are.

426
00:22:59,344 --> 00:23:00,777
Because you crashed
my workout?

427
00:23:00,846 --> 00:23:03,679
You're doing core training,
which improves balance,

428
00:23:03,749 --> 00:23:07,583
which staves off the most
debilitating symptoms of Huntington's.

429
00:23:07,652 --> 00:23:09,984
You've ended your
self-destructive streak.

430
00:23:10,055 --> 00:23:12,285
You want to do
something significant,

431
00:23:12,357 --> 00:23:16,259
something that'll last longer
than the few years you have left.

432
00:23:16,828 --> 00:23:18,853
My team is your
first, best choice.

433
00:23:18,930 --> 00:23:23,867
And my first choice is the community
health clinic I interviewed with yesterday.

434
00:23:23,935 --> 00:23:25,402
Absolutely,
you should do that.

435
00:23:25,470 --> 00:23:29,201
Three hours a week, every doctor
should, because every doctor can.

436
00:23:29,274 --> 00:23:31,367
But you don't want
to be every doctor.

437
00:23:31,443 --> 00:23:34,640
Plus, on my team, you
get to screw with Foreman.

438
00:23:35,313 --> 00:23:36,678
Every way but literally.

439
00:23:36,748 --> 00:23:38,875
Why are you
doing it this way?

440
00:23:39,317 --> 00:23:41,410
