asking us. Why?

442
00:23:43,955 --> 00:23:47,789
See, this is why you'd be
miserable wiping noses in a clinic.

443
00:23:49,361 --> 00:23:52,797
You can't ask because you
can't face the rejection.

444
00:23:52,864 --> 00:23:54,092
